parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The page number. Pages start from page 1. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: EventName
parameters.description:
The name of the alert.

*   Set the value to ALL, which indicates all alert types.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and response. Default value: **zh**. Valid values:

*   **zh**: Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Default value: 20.

parameters.name: Source
parameters.description: The feature to which this operation belongs. If you leave this parameter empty, the default value agentless is used.
